{"tid":1139500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗南亞幫球場開片　6人混戰玻璃樽作武器釀兩傷","createTime":"2019-05-05T10:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T11:36:15.000Z","uid":2748,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0e07deb2dda3cd65a2c6490fcbfea84028ff94f2","tid":1139500,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190505/photo/bkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190505175920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190505175920&h=fee8d58b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南亞兵團又作惡！今日(5日)下午3時許，4名南亞漢在擊壤路足球場飲酒，期間與兩同鄉因故發生口角，繼而動武釀成打鬥，4人追住對方毆打，有人掟垃圾桶及膠櫈。2名南亞漢不敵，圍住球場逃跑，他們逃出擊壤路後，有人檢起玻璃啤酒樽作武器進行打鬥，一時間叫喊聲、追遂打鬥聲此起彼落，途人見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報派多輛警車到場，截獲兩名頭部受傷南亞漢，4名南亞兇徒已四散逃去，救護員替傷者包紮後送院。現場遺下血漬及玻璃碎片，警方在現場調查毆鬥原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190505/photo/bkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190505175920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190505175920&h=cff0e2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190505/photo/bkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190505175920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190505175920&h=4ed587db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190505/photo/bkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190505175920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190505163145958-0505_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190505175920&h=7fcdb0ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https:/